{"tid":1615875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(遲來的Post) 有關101後轉職，詳細觀察，幫助轉職，下次再做好啲","createTime":"2019-10-03T08:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T12:24:23.000Z","uid":261661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3777aac37dee22352b9de793f324a784974dadbf","tid":1615875,"uid":261661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:32:14.000Z","msg":"(遲來的Post) 有關101後轉職，詳細觀察，幫助轉職，下次再做好啲<br />\n<br />\n香城Online 朋友代傳，朋友無ACC，以下是朋友的觀察及直播所得<br />\n朋友表示，佢係轉職企前小小無耐，所以十一副本後對自己都好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (佢以往只係自發做哨報消息、現場走幾條街傳資訊、帶物資居多。)<br />\n就佢既觀察，希望幫到大家轉職，同加快存經驗值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滅煙隊</span></span></strong><br />\n全民滅煙經驗值要升級，朋友第一次滅煙&hellip;失敗左，仲浪費左成支水！<br />\n見到有手足用防水袋 / 不鏽鋼水壺 (目測係只係細細個500ml左右size!)，將龍蛋掉入去shake 一shake就搞掂左！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (求巴絲 搵返啲比較有效既滅煙POST出黎)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n觀察係兩個步驟<br />\n１ 踩停粒龍蛋<br />\n２ 倒水降溫<br />\n３ 有手套下快速執起龍蛋掉入防水袋 / 不鏽鋼水壺<br />\n４ Shake!<br />\n當然手足係戴左泳鏡防毒。當時係灣仔大逃亡中，條條路都有魔物企係天橋上面射龍蛋 (地面係無魔物，但全世界恐懼大於一切&hellip;) 最後走無可走要突圍出去，全地TG全地煙，極高濃度，有豬咀泳鏡都有小小頂唔到，皮膚極灼熱！有好幾次見到有人想滅煙，但粒龍蛋比人執左掉反出去，又有時見到啲龍蛋多到滅煙隊滅唔切。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友話建議：見到大規模既龍蛋，先好掉返出去，得數粒就比滅煙隊滅左佢！<br />\n紿終啲煙無咁濃，對手足有利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">石匠</span></span></strong><br />\n點樣開發土地同點削石，成塊完整磚2.5KG，(傳送左粒回城研究)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，真係拋得唔遠，要改進，要有後援既石匠打造，下次再玩ONLINE GAME開個新角色做石匠，研究緊角色攻略，睇下可唔可以增加土魔法射程。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次朋友個朋友個朋友話見到有人拎到移動力+10既購物車，點解可以做到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對土系魔法師好重要。MP可以有效補給。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工兵路障隊</span></span></strong><br />\n帶士巴拿，一定要2支！<br />\n開一個欄要兩邊螺絲帽都用士巴拿，要用可以調校螺絲帽尺寸果隻。拆左其中一邊螺絲帽後，可用槓桿原理拉爆對邊既螺絲帽，咁會快速啲。<br />\n帶多啲索帶，收集現場索帶都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時用士巴拿可以搵到隱藏既+10裝備防盾材料<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聞說有進化左既水系&mdash;&mdash;聖水魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n聖水魔法師，有驅魔既效果，魔物中左聖水後會呈溶解既狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖水魔法師 ＡＮＤ 火魔法師，都係門檻較高，射程唔遠，心理壓力大。<br />\n新手或者用住土系先，比較易掌握，又可以快速刷經驗 （要配合石匠）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">＊＊補充＊＊射程資料＊＊</span></span></strong><br />\n袋袋彈range 20m 一個籃球場<br />\nSponge bullet 40m 半個7人足球場<br />\nRubber bullet 65m 一個7人足球場<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">雨傘對呢袋袋彈Sponge都係有效地減到速度同殺傷力 (因為係鈍器創傷)，Rubber有多小小穿透力所以唔知</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">其實依家大部份人都有晒基本盤GEAR (泳境 + 防毒 + 頭盔)<br />\n係差 現場經驗 同 轉職攻略 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出門執野時，要諗自己係咩角色，帶相應道具，然後專心做好。<br />\n有時臨場都要立即搵到自己角色啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉職選擇</span></span></strong>　<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防護師 &ndash; 睇前面 / 後方需要舉傘，做屏蔽 / 掩護 / 防禦<br />\n工匠 &ndash; 現場製作裝備 (無呢方面知識)<br />\n石匠 &ndash; 造石<br />\n滅煙 &ndash; 收拾龍蛋<br />\n哨兵 &ndash; 自發的話，可一身輕裝 (N95 / Cap帽 / 泳鏡)，跑多幾條街，帶望遠鏡8x or 12x 迪記，帶個小喇叭，四圍問人啲街道咩情況，跑過去求證 (對跑友一流)，搵不在場朋友幫你mon 新聞直播，將1手消息現場廣傳，盡量9成都用1手消息，<br />\n魔法師 / 戰士 - 無呢方面知識<br />\n各種有效道具：索帶，交剪，保鮮紙好似少左聽人叫，六角匙 (唔知咩SIZE)，士巴拿 (可較尺寸果種)，望遠鏡，傘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即場士氣同埋即場心態好重要，要有基本還拖既心理準備。如果唔係會變大潰敗！<br />\n最後，對唔住，下次會再做好啲。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">.........................................................................</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為左培養大家有多小小自衛反擊既心態，同埋多小小勇敢，做多啲嘗試</span></span></strong><br />\n以後口號叫香港人！！你既回應要係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還拖</span></span></strong>！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人!!!  還拖!!! </span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人!!!  還拖!!! </span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2138d1a990953e56ba3265a2c16662380b5fc95c","tid":1615875,"uid":261661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">.........................................................................</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為左培養大家有多小小自衛反擊既心態，同埋多小小勇敢，做多啲嘗試</span></span></strong><br />\n以後口號叫香港人！！你既回應要係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還拖</span></span></strong>！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人!!!  還拖!!! </span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人!!!  還拖!!! </span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c7a05f182de2d7c02cf2403140d986f07e8415","tid":1615875,"uid":261661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">.........................................................................</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為左培養大家有多小小自衛反擊既心態，同埋多小小勇敢，做多啲嘗試</span></span></strong><br />\n以後口號叫香港人！！你既回應要係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還拖</span></span></strong>！！<br